metadata.name: SHIWA World Cup Qatar 2022 - Al-Dawsari Saudi Arabia
metadata.description:
Saudi Arabia Star.

The sporting event of the year is here. The World Cup starts in Qatar. An exotic location where the stars of world soccer will meet during the tournament that will leave us a new world champion! Choose your favorite NFT and follow the world cup full of surprises with Shiwa Finance.

80% of the proceeds of this collection will be send to shiwafoundation.eth to finance the listing of the SHIWA token in centralized exchanges, the best way to support the growth of SHIWA and get in return an epic collectible.
